  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Written informed consent obtained.

          -  Documented diagnosis of asthma and/or COPD (a range of different severities for both
             diseases).

          -  Age: 6 years or above.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Any severe chronic respiratory disease other than asthma or COPD.

          -  Acute respiratory infection.

          -  Concurrent participation in a clinical drug study.

          -  Inability to perform repeatable spirometric measurements.

          -  Any medical condition that in the opinion of the investigator would endanger the
             subject if he/she participates in the study (such as contraindications to spirometry).
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
